						"active": false,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "Hello [~s.volkov],\r\nWe tested the issue you reported. The calendar is working as expected with horizontal and vertical mode on device Huawei y9 2018 (android 8) and  Huawei Gr3 2017 (android 7).\r\n\r\n*Android 8:*\r\n !1569750810528.JPEG|thumbnail!  !1569750969144.JPEG|thumbnail! \r\n\r\n\r\n*Android 7:*\r\n!potrait_7.png|thumbnail!  !landscape_7.png|thumbnail!  \r\n\r\nWhich device are you using?",
					"updateAuthor": {
						"name": "rmitro",
						"key": "rmitro",
						"displayName": "Rakhi Mitro",
						"active": false,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
